&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced&lt;strong&gt; Administrative Assistant&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;for an &lt;strong&gt;in-office role&lt;/strong&gt; in our Rye Brook, NY office to support our Field Operations and Self-Perform departments.&lt;/p&gt;
