&lt;li&gt;Strong MS Office skills: &amp;nbsp;Excel, Word, PowerPoint, and Outlook skills required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to multitask, prioritize, and manage work on tight deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High level of professionalism and confidentiality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team-player and ability to build relationships across the organization and team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
